<h2>Grapefruit Popsicles</h2>

<div class="row">
  <div class="column" style="background-color:#ECC4BB;">
  <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <p>-Grapefruit Juice
    <br>-Water
    <br>-Mold of your choice
    <br>-Popsicle Stick
    <br>-A Freezer
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="column" style="background-color:#ECC4BB;">
    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <p>First mix your juice and your wate and have it 85% juice and 15% water. The put it into your molder with a popsicle stick in it to get it out. Put it in your freezer for about 2-3 hours and then enjoy and send us a pic ;)</p>
